    "We show in Table 2, our safety risk taxonomy.",
    "The detailed taxonomy and guidelines as used to train models can be found in the later subsections.",
    "Our safety policy is referred to throughout the annotation process.",
    "We do not claim that our taxonomy and safety policy are comprehensive, and that the model trained with this mitigates all potential risks.",
    "However, we cover a broad spectrum of relevant risks that should be general enough for applying safeguards in place."
